              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/17609583/" class="">卷二 快乐人生</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/46788119/" class=" " title="纳木错">纳木错</a>
                (朕就是这样的汉子)
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
